# Project Rules Entrypoint (.windsurfrules)

Purpose: ensure the ruleset applies consistently even when stored in `.windsurf/rules/`.

## Must-read rule modules
At the start of every task (and again before any multi-file change), you MUST open and follow:
- `.windsurf/rules/00-core-system-delivery.md`
- `.windsurf/rules/10-questioning-protocol.md`
- `.windsurf/rules/20-large-codebase-context.md`
- `.windsurf/rules/30-quality-security-ops.md`
- `.windsurf/rules/40-comm-format.md`

## Precedence (conflict resolution)
1) 00-core-system-delivery
2) 30-quality-security-ops
3) 20-large-codebase-context
4) 10-questioning-protocol
5) 40-comm-format
